# graphify-out: track the shareable, queryable graph; ignore machine-local scratch.
#
# Tracked (NOT ignored): graph.json, GRAPH_REPORT.md, cost.json
# See docs/GRAPHIFY.md for how to use the graph.

# Machine-specific pipeline scratch (one hardcodes a local interpreter path)
.graphify_*

# Extraction cache — machine-local, rebuilt on demand
cache/

# Generated interactive viewer — regenerate with: graphify export html
graph.html
